text: Abdoulkader Kamil Mohamed () (born 1 July 1952) is a Djiboutian politician. He became the Prime Minister of Djibouti in April 2013. He originates from the Warsangeli clan located in Somalia. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Djibouti Category:Current national leaders
title: Abdoulkader Kamil Mohamed
